Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Is anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people drank that red wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm drinking it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the bodyguards that were supposed to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to be on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to look for your sister and bring her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already located her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me, your sister will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go the way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everything is going according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster I thought was inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:29.95,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(392,100)\pos(327,343)}Johan's Footprints
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for coming this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Nina Fortner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Fortner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Nina Fortner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked you to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as The Baby said, she's not your average girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here on orders from The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's d...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek was the one who told us to bring you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we took you hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you to see Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to search the residence of Milan Kolasch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is suspected in the shooting at\Nthe Rodelheim Convention Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Kolasch's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will come to search the house soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Milan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Milan really die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan died for our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek killed our families...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he tried to take revenge, and got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Milan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan wouldn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge leads to revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just go back and forth, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan wouldn't have wanted you to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan was trying to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Milan truly want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To travel with everyone and visit all of our hometowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dream will come true someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me stay, Mr. Mustafa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Minh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Suleiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your delicious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of material regarding\Na man named Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan Kolasch was after {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find this man as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to question him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Kaiser Hotel, a man known as "The Baby"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the leader of an extreme right organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been found murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young man coming in and out\Nof this hotel with Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the devil's disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, you are... Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.79,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:56.96,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or his sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan has kept me alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the one who is going to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just whose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose plan is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan was here, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go outside now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's still going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I hadn't led you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the banquet hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching this apartment for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ear! My ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be your ear next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christoph Sievernich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'd already heard of your late father, Ernest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Frankfurt... no, in Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Sievernich financial group\Nis one of the largest powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that you're the heir to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek trying to do by\Nbringing you and Johan together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bleeding too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me treat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I start...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I led you to that devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek thinks he's the one who brought us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Johan and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were friends a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek doesn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were friends in East Berlin over ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in East Berlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sievernich's adopted son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sold by an agent on the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where Johan and I first met was in East Berlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,511...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to know each other there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only he and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they're done killing each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten real quiet outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go crazy if we stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's fine, come back and let us know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on that day, everyone at Kinderheim 511 went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the children. The instructors\Nalso started killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have escaped, leaving us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm lying, go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be eating a warm meal by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warm meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't betray me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come back, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hide forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry and thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drifted in and out of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big joke that {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek thinks it's his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about it thousands of times when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot my ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A politician's face is his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Johan's help, I'm going to make the world mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about my ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spoil my plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When my sister arrives, tell her where I am."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"After that, my sister will kill me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regained all of your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is full of hatred, anger and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sadness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you twins were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:30.96,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:44.39,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:44.39,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:47.35,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:23:01.03,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:23:01.03,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:25.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:34.31,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:36.77,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
